<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <h1>Shipping and Delivery Policy</h1>

  <p>At <strong>BlueBazaar.store</strong>, we are committed to delivering your orders quickly, safely, and efficiently. Please read our shipping and delivery policy carefully.</p>

  <h2>1. Shipping Coverage</h2>
  <p>We currently deliver across all major cities and towns in India. If your location is not serviceable, we will inform you during checkout or via email.</p>

  <h2>2. Order Processing Time</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>All orders are processed within <strong>1–2 business days</strong> (excluding Sundays and public holidays).</li>
    <li>You will receive an order confirmation via email or SMS after placing your order.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Delivery Time</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Estimated delivery time: <strong>3–7 business days</strong> from the date of dispatch, depending on your location.</li>
    <li>Delays may occur due to weather, festivals, logistics issues, or unforeseen circumstances.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Shipping Charges</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>We offer <strong>free shipping</strong> on all prepaid orders above ₹499.</li>
    <li>For orders below ₹499, a standard shipping charge may apply and will be shown at checkout.</li>
    <li>Cash on Delivery (COD) orders may include an additional charge.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Tracking Your Order</h2>
  <p>Once your order is shipped, we will provide a tracking ID via email or SMS. You can use this ID to track your order status on the courier partner’s website.</p>

  <h2>6. Delivery Partners</h2>
  <p>We partner with trusted courier services like Delhivery, BlueDart, Ekart, Xpressbees, etc., to ensure timely and safe delivery.</p>

  <h2>7. Failed Delivery Attempts</h2>
  <p>If a delivery attempt fails due to an incorrect address, unavailability, or rejection, the package may be returned to us. In such cases, re-delivery will be subject to additional charges.</p>

  <h2>8. Damaged or Missing Items</h2>
  <p>If you receive a damaged package or any item is missing, please contact us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of delivery at <a href="mailto:support@bluebazaar.store">support@bluebazaar.store</a> with photos/videos as proof.</p>

  <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions regarding shipping or delivery, feel free to reach out:</p>
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@bluebazaar.store">support@bluebazaar.store</a></p>

  <p><em>Last Updated: August 7, 2025</em></p>
</body>
